snippet.textDisplay: Guys this song is related to rajsthaan..... In this song deval charani is the mother of Lord karni ma..... And deval ma gave a horse to pabuji rathore (lok devta of rajsthaan) as a gift..... And other side the brother in law of pabuji rathore was demanding that horse which got pabuji rathore from deval ma then the brother in law of pabuji he kept all the cows of deval mata...... So in this song deval mata says to pabuji release my cows from ur brother in law..... When pabuji was going to do marriage...... Marvellous song
